data.description: Live your Dream!! This Stunning all block construction home awaits you in the Highly sought after Blue Springs Park area of Volusia county. Perfect floor plan that flows with 3 large bedrooms and 2 well appointed baths with a spacious 2 car garage. The large kitchen boasts a breakfast bar with adjoining dining room great for entertaining. Main living area is very open and features volume ceilings.You'll love the decorative niches, stylish ceiling fans, and abundant Closet space. An inside utility room makes housework a breeze.Tile floors throughout the home, and a trussed screen porch for enjoying those summer evenings. Don't miss out on this affordable opportunity. **SELLER IS OFFERING $3500 towards BUYERS CLOSING COSTS! Make your appointment today!
